    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"280891\">@Frank Steffahn</span> I don't think your first example is UB - the <code>ptr::swap</code> docs explicitly state that overlapping is allowed</p>",
        "id": 239301377,
